(17073, 654, 'content_1_content_2_dynamic_media_text', '<h4>NEC Takes Over the Peak</h4>\r\nSince 2015 NEC spends a winter afternoon at Pat’s Peak. Students, faculty, and staff enjoy free skiing, snowboarding, tubing, free a, and rentals for the day. There are plenty of inside activities as well; music, food, drinks, and bingo. NEC Takes Over the Peak is scheduled for Wednesday, February 13, 2019.'),
