(17099, 654, 'content_1_content_4_dynamic_media_text', '<h4>Up All Night</h4>\r\nUp All Night celebrates the end of the fall academic semester. Student organizations all sponsor a variety of activities for 12 hours of fun on campus, all through the night. Dodgeball, crafts, karaoke, movies, and human foosball are just some of the activities at this event the past few years.'),
