(17536, 682, 'content_1_content_0_dynamic_text_content', '<h3>My Accounts</h3>\r\nWe urge you to come for a visit to completely understand what New England College has to offer you. It is a small, yet very integrated community. It’s a place where the environment and the outdoors are front and center, from the Contoocook River meandering through campus, to wooded trails for hiking, snow shoeing, and cross country skiing nestled between classroom buildings and sport fields. Downhill skiing at Pat’s Peak is also a few short minutes away.'),
