(18129, 48, 'content_1_content_3_dynamic_text_content', '<h3>Parent Fund</h3>\r\nNew England College realizes its mission of experiential learning and transformational education in part through the involvement of parents like you. Giving to the Parent Fund enables you to have a lasting impact on the school that you and your student love. Gifts to the Parent Fund are spent in the year they are received as part of NEC\'s annual fundraising. The purpose of these contributions is to support the college above and beyond tuition dollars. Your gift to the Parent Fund supports study-away trips, career and academic success services, on-campus events, and the other vital NEC programs that help our students achieve their goals.'),
